Package r7.sabre.spaces.distance

Class DistanceMatrix

java.lang.Object
r7.sabre.spaces.distance.DistanceMatrix
public class DistanceMatrix extends Object
A distance matrix calculates the distance between each pair of stories in a given solution set according to the given distance metric.
